title: Getting Started - Example Documentation
content:
Getting Started with Example Platform

Welcome to the Example Platform documentation. This guide will help you get started quickly.

Installation

To install the platform, run the following command:

pip install example-platform

Quick Start

Here's a simple example to get you started:

from example import Platform

platform = Platform()
platform.initialize()
platform.run()
